Package com.iritech.mirisreg704

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NativeHelper
    This class is a helper for communicate with iris-service at JNI.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BiographicInfo
    The BiographicInfo class is used to store biographic information of person.
    EyeSubtype
    This class enumerates which eye (left or right) a captured image or a generated template is from.
    GalleryInfo
    This class describe the information detail from the gallery.
    IRegCode
    This class enumerates all error codes about user gallery.
    IRegSetting
    Contains all configuration parameters of IriTech devices supported.
    IrisReg
    this class defines the methods for matching and enroll irises.
    MatchResult
    This class defines the interface for storing result matching.
    TemplateInfo
    This class reveals basic information of a template such as versions, number of left irises, number of right irises, number of unknown irises, or total irises.
